text.tspan: Yeah, that's me! I'm Heather, and I'm a skeleton. Kinda.
Here's the weird part. I'm technically not one; I'm a
human being who just so happens to have completely
transparent skin, muscle tissue, and organs, but not
bones! Weird, right? Any clothes I put on also
turn invisible, and they don't seem to turn back at all.
Ever. This is inconvenient when I try to remember
where I put all my clothes. I guess the universe just
hates me. I suspect Anastasia is the one responsible
for whatever made me this way, but I've never asked
her because I guess don't really want to know.
Anyways, I'm an amateur photographer of sorts, and I
also write records of the mansion for fun, as if people
want to know the history of this place. I know this
mansion almost too well: I have mapped out every
nook, cranny, and secret passage in this place!
Heather
That's me!
Age: 21
Species: Human
Alignment: Good
